Value List T_CONT (\d+)
Value DBA_PROFILE_ID (\d+)
		
Start
  ^\s*Notes:\s*\*\s*indicates\s*Discrete\s*TCONT\(TCONT\s*Unbound\)\s* -> TCONTS

TCONTS
  ^\s*-+
  ^\s+<T-CONT\s+$T_CONT>\s+DBA\s*Profile-ID:\s*$DBA_PROFILE_ID\s*$$ -> Record
  ^\s*<Gem\s*Index\s*\d+\s*>\s*$$ -> End
  ^\s*$$
  ^. -> Error

End